{"tid":210828,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發] 伊奧古死咗","createTime":"2017-04-21T08:29:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-21T15:44:29.000Z","uid":29167,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d217902f9494c9fecf1497f6a49b74c7b2f9d156","tid":210828,"uid":29167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T08:29:10.000Z","msg":"Ugo Ehiogu dies aged 44 after collapsing at Tottenham's training ground<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://e1.365dm.com/17/04/16-9/20/skysports-ugo-ehiogu-ehiogu-obituary-sky-sports-news_3935448.jpg?20170421082602\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fe1.365dm.com%2F17%2F04%2F16-9%2F20%2Fskysports-ugo-ehiogu-ehiogu-obituary-sky-sports-news_3935448.jpg%3F20170421082602&h=fc12844f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nFormer England international Ugo Ehiogu has died at the age of 44 after collapsing at Tottenham's training ground.<br />\n<br />\nEhiogu had been working as an U23 coach at Spurs and was rushed to hospital after suffering a heart attack on Thursday.<br />\n<br />\nA statement from Spurs, released on Friday, announced Ehiogu passed away &quot;in the early hours of this morning&quot;.<br />\n<br />\nThe statement read: &quot;It is with immense sadness we announce the passing of Ugo Ehiogu.<br />\n<br />\n&quot;Ugo received immediate treatment after suffering a cardiac arrest at the training centre yesterday before being transferred to hospital, where he passed away in the early hours of this morning.&quot;<br />\n<br />\nSpurs' head of coaching and player development John McDermott said: &quot;Words cannot express the shock and sadness that we all feel at the club.<br />\n<br />\n&quot;Ugo's immense presence will be irreplaceable. Our heartfelt sympathies go out to his wife Gemma and his family.&quot;<br />\n<br />\nEhiogu had been working as a Tottenham coach since 2014<br />\nEhiogu had been working as a Tottenham coach since 2014<br />\nEhiogu won four England caps during a 20-year playing career spent largely at Aston Villa and Middlesbrough.<br />\n<br />\nThe centre-half spent nine years at Villa and seven on Teesside, winning the League Cup with both and helping Villa reach the FA Cup final in 2000 - the last at the old Wembley.<br />\n<br />\nHe also played for West Brom, Rangers, Leeds and Sheffield United and joined the Spurs coaching staff in 2014.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.skysports.com/football/news/11095/10844711/ugo-ehiogu-dies-aged-44-after-collapsing-at-tottenhams-training-ground\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.skysports.com%2Ffootball%2Fnews%2F11095%2F10844711%2Fugo-ehiogu-dies-aged-44-after-collapsing-at-tottenhams-training-ground&d=fc%2FsVbAXSk%2FqMRyYewxCuAEk2Noh57F05xbgvjQdsX8%3D&h=826b474e\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.skysports.com/football/news/11095/10844711/ugo-ehiogu-dies-aged-44-after-collapsing-at-tottenhams-training-ground</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04c1f1f00cb3be55474c88e5542deb8f2af064e6","tid":210828,"uid":54747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T08:30:57.000Z","msg":"下，咁震撼<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"069bd04b0e7e75c4be19cea2af7ab1da8dca3840","tid":210828,"uid":36142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T08:32:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11e75a04e0de