aces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9929a2853d62b56e022ddfd2f3d5ec5954618168","tid":210828,"uid":29167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T08:43:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>修夫基個friend<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Q5R0Q6g.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQ5R0Q6g.png&h=a188ba12&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n米舖都出咗post 悼念 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當年佢＋修夫基 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"843fa14690d794d884978d5f0a80b63159f8ff60","tid":210828,"uid":91875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T08:46:19.000Z","msg":"RIP<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b42d503e4889962ea5715d45a9b987adac6f1c4a","tid":210828,"uid":29167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T08:46:49.000Z","msg":"伊奧古病逝終年44歲<br />\n<br />\n【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=fc%2FsVbAXSk%2FqMRyYewxCuAEk2Noh57F05xbgvjQdsX8%3D&h=a3e09910\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】前英格蘭國家隊及阿士東維拉後衛伊奧古因心臟病逝世，終年44歲。<br />\n<br />\n熱刺於周五發表聲明，公佈伊奧古的死訊。<br />\n<br />\n早於周四，熱刺發出官方新聞稿，懷疑這位前英格蘭國腳心臟病發：「我們可以確認，伊奧古今日較早時間在訓練中心暈倒，目前正在醫院。我們的U23教練即場接受了軍醫的治理，之後被救護車送到醫院。球會各人向伊奧古及其家人送上祝福。當我們得到進一步資訊，屆時將會再向大家更新情況。」<br />\n<br />\n44歲的伊奧古，球員生涯先後效力過阿士東維拉、米杜士堡和西布朗等球隊，並曾為英格蘭國家隊披甲4次。伊奧古2009年掛靴，之後曾成為英格蘭U20代表隊教練團成員；本來以兼職身分在熱刺工作的他，2014年正式加入，擔任熱刺青年軍教練。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://sports.now.com/home/news/details?id=17828296283\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsports.now.com%2Fhome%2Fnews%2Fdetails%3Fid%3D17828296283&d=fc%2FsVbAXSk%2FqMRyYewxCuAEk2Noh57F05xbgvjQdsX8%3D&h=7e60ffdd\" target=\"_blank\">http://sports.now.com/home/news/details?id=17828296283</a>"},{"pid":"6b0badf6c76efd557abfb89c720eff14bd503e1c",